    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "何路通",
        "李玉",
        "杨香武",
        "计全"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全、何路通同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在衙中奉了大人命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寻找令牌要小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全、何路通",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺——（计全）（何路通）。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我奉了大人之命寻找金牌。看前面已是薛家窝，你我还是与那厮前去拜寿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是越庄而过？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我去至他庄，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二人催马往前拥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又只见二位老英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨香武、李玉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是杨、李二位老英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是计全。此位是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是何路通。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，见过二位老英雄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见二位老英雄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢么就是人称“赛鱼鹰”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令师可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已下世了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！又去了一位老英雄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知二位老英雄打从哪道而来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打从薛家窝而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老英雄，为何与那厮来往？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我二人亦是为金牌之事而来。只因我二人在酒楼饮酒，见关泰、谢永泰被他们"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擒去，故而以拜寿为名，前去探听。那薛金龙将关泰二人吊在马棚之内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何路通听令！今晚三更十分，去到他庄马棚之内，搭救他二人，不得有误！回"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去对天霸言讲，上你一件功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（何路通下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面有一包头镇，就是凤凰张七住处，去到那里访问金牌下落，便知明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到此时我这才把宽心来放，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李玉",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寻访金牌为忠良。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨香武、李玉同下。）"
        }
      ],
