      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛金龙、四下手、黄天霸、关泰、谢永泰、何路通、计全自两边分上，同对阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛金龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，你是何人，敢挡老夫的去路？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就瞎了你的狗眼！你老爷家住江南绍兴府金华县，四霸天赛罗成，黄天霸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛金龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天霸，你父三泰也是绿林中的英雄。不想生了你这逆子，投在赃官手下，每每"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛金龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与绿林作对，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛金龙，老匹夫！你既在这薛家窝居住，就该安分守己，才是正理，为何每每"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与总漕大人干涉？今日特奉大人之命，前来拿你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛金龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你拿老夫什么过犯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你将关泰、谢永泰吊在马棚，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛金龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也是老夫一时大意，被你等救去。今日老夫饶尔等不死，去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你黄爷有好生之德，快快就擒，免在刀下做鬼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛金龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得胡言，看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、薛金龙同起打。连环十二股荡。薛金龙被擒，黄天霸三笑。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
